statements: SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Analytics;
SELECT session_id, user_id, event_type, event_time, event_data FROM AR_VR_Analytics;
SELECT user_id, event_type, session_id, event_time, event_data FROM AR_VR_Analytics;
SELECT event_type, session_id, event_time, user_id, event_data FROM AR_VR_Analytics;
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Analytics ORDER BY event_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Analytics WHERE user_id = 12345;
SELECT user_id, event_type, event_time FROM AR_VR_Analytics WHERE session_id = '719d8e9e-88e4-4c71-91f1-7ef2011975bb';
SELECT session_id, event_type, event_time FROM AR_VR_Analytics WHERE user_id = 54321 ORDER BY event_time DESC;
SELECT user_id, event_type, COUNT(*) AS event_count FROM AR_VR_Analytics GROUP BY user_id, event_type;
SELECT user_id, event_type, event_time FROM AR_VR_Analytics WHERE session_id = '0d29acac-4cd7-4323-b816-6d35d16b5807' AND event_type LIKE '%click%' ORDER BY event_time ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Analytics;
SELECT user_id, event_name, event_timestamp FROM AR_VR_Analytics WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT session_id, event_name FROM AR_VR_Analytics WHERE session_id = 456;
SELECT user_id, performance_metric, performance_value FROM Performance_Tracking WHERE user_id = 789;
SELECT session_id, performance_metric, performance_value FROM Performance_Tracking WHERE performance_value > 50;
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Analytics ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, session_id, performance_value FROM Performance_Tracking WHERE performance_metric = 'fps' ORDER BY performance_value DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT event_name, COUNT(*) as event_count FROM AR_VR_Analytics GROUP BY event_name ORDER BY event_count DESC;
SELECT user_id, AVG(performance_value) as avg_performance FROM Performance_Tracking GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY avg_performance DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT user_id, session_id, performance_metric, event_name FROM Performance_Tracking INNER JOIN AR_VR_Analytics ON Performance_Tracking.user_id = AR_VR_Analytics.user_id ORDER BY user_id ASC, session_id DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_name, user_email FROM AR_VR_Users;
SELECT session_id, session_duration, session_date FROM AR_VR_Sessions ORDER BY session_date DESC;
SELECT user_name, last_login_date FROM AR_VR_Users WHERE last_login_date > '2021-01-01' ORDER BY last_login_date ASC;
SELECT performance_id, render_time, frame_rate, memory_usage FROM AR_VR_Performance WHERE memory_usage > 1024;

SELECT AR_VR_Users.user_name, AR_VR_Sessions.session_date, AR_VR_Performance.frame_rate FROM AR_VR_Users JOIN AR_VR_Sessions ON AR_VR_Users.user_id = AR_VR_Sessions.user_id JOIN AR_VR_Performance ON AR_VR_Sessions.session_id = AR_VR_Performance.session_id ORDER BY AR_VR_Sessions.session_date DESC;
SELECT user_id, user_name, user_email FROM AR_VR_Users ORDER BY user_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Sessions WHERE session_duration > 10 AND session_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT user_name, session_date, render_time FROM AR_VR_Users JOIN AR_VR_Sessions ON AR_VR_Users.user_id = AR_VR_Sessions.user_id WHERE render_time > 50 ORDER BY session_date DESC;

SELECT user_name, session_date, frame_rate FROM AR_VR_Users INNER JOIN AR_VR_Sessions ON AR_VR_Users.user_id = AR_VR_Sessions.user_id INNER JOIN AR_VR_Performance ON AR_VR_Sessions.session_id = AR_VR_Performance.session_id WHERE frame_rate < 30 ORDER BY user_name ASC, session_date ASC;

SELECT u.user_name, p.render_time, s.session_duration FROM AR_VR_Users u LEFT JOIN AR_VR_Sessions s ON u.user_id = s.user_id LEFT JOIN AR_VR_Performance p ON s.session_id = p.session_id WHERE p.render_time > 20 AND s.session_duration BETWEEN 5 AND 15 ORDER BY u.user_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Users;
SELECT user_id, username, age FROM AR_VR_Users WHERE age > 25;
SELECT event_id, event_type, event_timestamp FROM AR_VR_Events ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, performance_metric, performance_value FROM AR_VR_Performance WHERE performance_value > 0.8;
SELECT analytics_id, user_id, event_id FROM AR_VR_Analytics WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Users WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY username DESC
SELECT user_id, age, location FROM AR_VR_Users WHERE gender = 'Male' ORDER BY age ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT event_id, event_type, event_timestamp FROM AR_VR_Events WHERE event_timestamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL 1 DAY ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC
SELECT user_id, session_id, performance_metric FROM AR_VR_Performance WHERE performance_value > 0.8 ORDER BY performance_value DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT analytics_id, event_id, user_id FROM AR_VR_Analytics WHERE analytics_data->'$.session_duration' > 600 ORDER BY analytics_id ASC
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Users;
SELECT user_name, user_age, user_gender FROM AR_VR_Users ORDER BY user_age DESC;
SELECT event_type, event_timestamp FROM AR_VR_Events WHERE event_timestamp >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT session_id, session_start, session_end, session_duration FROM AR_VR_Sessions WHERE session_start <= '2022-01-31';
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Performance WHERE fps_avg > 60 AND cpu_usage < 50;
SELECT * FROM AR_VR_Users;
SELECT user_id, user_name, user_age FROM AR_VR_Users WHERE user_age > 25 ORDER BY user_age DESC;
SELECT session_id, session_start, session_end, session_duration FROM AR_VR_Sessions WHERE session_start > '2021-01-01' ORDER BY session_start DESC;
SELECT event_id, event_type, event_timestamp, AR_VR_Users.user_name FROM AR_VR_Events JOIN AR_VR_Users ON AR_VR_Events.session_id = AR_VR_Users.user_id;
SELECT AVG(fps_avg) AS avg_fps, AVG(cpu_usage) AS avg_cpu_usage FROM AR_VR_Performance WHERE gpu_usage > 50 GROUP BY session_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
